title: Tyra Banks is Personally Spearheading the Campaign to Get Tiffany Haddish to Host the Oscars

meta_data.description: Tiffany Haddish was a standout in an otherwise pretty bland Academy Awards and it has people, including Tyra Banks, trying to get her the hosting gig for next year.
